| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5680 — Recovery Inhibition (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5a14999c-e8c1-5507-afd9-e4cffac7d3ea"
